msgid "Master Barker"
msgstr "Vocero maestro"

msgctxt "1912"
msgid "Talk_OK"
msgstr "Talk_OK"

msgctxt "1916"
msgid "Using [Action:Button_L3@Adventure] and [Action:Button_R3@Adventure] buttons"
msgstr "Usa los botones [Action:Button_L3@Adventure] y [Action:Button_R3@Adventure]"

msgctxt "1920"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "56_Master Barker"
msgid "Watch carefully, figure out which person'll come with ya, keep your eyes trained on them and them alone, and go in for the chase! That's how to be a good barker."
msgstr "Observa atentamente e identifica a los potenciales clientes, mantén la vista fija en ellos y sigue sus pasos. ¡Traza el camino y ve a por él! ¡Eso es lo que hace un buen vocero!"

msgctxt "68_Using [Action:Button_L3@Adventure] and [Action:Button_R3@Adventure] buttons"
msgid "Input <Action:Button_L3@Adventure> and <Action:Button_R3@Adventure> by <Color:14>pressing the <Action:Button_L3@Adventure> or <Action:Button_R3@Adventure><Color:Default>."
msgstr "Para usar <Action:Button_L3@Adventure> y <Action:Button_R3@Adventure> debes de <Color:14>presionar el botón <Action:Button_L3@Adventure> o <Action:Button_R3@Adventure><Color:Default>."

msgctxt "80_Using [Action:Button_L3@Adventure] and [Action:Button_R3@Adventure] buttons"
msgid "<Action:Button_L3@Adventure> is used to zoom in and out of the minimap.\\r\n"
"<Action:Button_R3@Adventure> is used to enter first-person mode."
msgstr "<Action:Button_L3@Adventure> se utiliza para acercar y alejar el minimapa.\\r\n"
"<Action:Button_R3@Adventure> se utiliza para entrar en el modo en primera persona."

msgctxt "92_Using [Action:Button_L3@Adventure] and [Action:Button_R3@Adventure] buttons"
msgid "This information has been added as a <Color:14>memo<Color:Default>.\\r\n"
"Read <Color:14>memos<Color:Default> by selecting <Color:14>Memos<Color:Default> in the Pause Menu.\\r\n"
"You can access the Pause Menu with the <Action:Button_Options@Adventure> button."
msgstr "Esta información ha sido añadida como una <Color:14>nota<Color:Default>.\\r\n"
"Lee las <Color:14>notas<Color:Default> seleccionando <Color:14>Notas<Color:Default> en el menú de pausa.\\r\n"
"Puedes acceder al menú de pausa con el botón <Action:Button_Options@Adventure>."

msgctxt "104_Master Barker"
msgid "If you're trippin' up while you keep lookin' at a potential customer, then you're still an amateur."
msgstr "Si te tropiezas mientras observas y sigues a un cliente potencial, significa que eres un novato."

